@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### 1. 测试用户注册 - 有效数据
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstname": "John",
  "lastname": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2. 测试用户注册 - 无效数据（空字段）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstname": "",
  "lastname": "",
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "password": "123"
}

### 3. 测试用户注册 - 重复邮箱
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/register  
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstname": "Jane",
  "lastname": "Smith",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "654321"
}

### 4. 测试用户登录 - 正确凭据
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 5. 测试用户登录 - 错误密码
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 6. 测试用户登录 - 不存在的用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "notexist@example.com",
  "password": "anypassword"
}

### 7. 测试无效 JSON 格式
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstname": "Test"
  "lastname": "User"  // 故意缺少逗号
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 8. 测试缺少 Content-Type
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/register

{
  "firstname": "Test",
  "lastname": "User",
  "email": "test2@example.com",
  "password": "123456"
}